The paper uses convolutional neural networks (CNN) for image representation learning, which is a common technique in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also employs multi-instance multi-task learning, which is a popular approach in machine learning (cs.LG). The study involves reasoning and understanding body conditions, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with medical data and patient records, which is relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the paper involves data analysis and classification, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
